author: The Current
description:
Justin Courtney Pierre of Motion City Soundtrack talking about the unique perspective that young bands can use to their advantage.

He mentions Patrick Stump of Fall Out Boy, who is featured on their song "Particle Physics" off of their latest album 'The Same Old Wasted Wonderful World.'
